==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ki-]]'' (interrogative and relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-al]]'' (correlative suffix of reason)

===Correlative===
'''kial'''
# [[why]] (interrogative and relative correlative of reason)
#: Like other interrogative and relative correlatives, '''kial''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Kial''' ajn'' thus means ''why ever''.

===Derived words===
